    AgentInterface
    The AgentInterface defines the remote interface for interacting with agents in a distributed opinion retrieval system using Java RMI (Remote Method Invocation).

    The ServerInterface defines the remote interface for managing agents and topics in a distributed opinion retrieval system using Java RMI (Remote Method Invocation).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Agent
    The Agent class represents an abstract agent in a distributed opinion retrieval system using Java RMI (Remote Method Invocation).
    ConsensusFinder
    The ConsensusFinder class facilitates the consensus process between two agents on a specified topic using Java sockets for direct communication.
    CriticalThinker
    The CriticalThinker class represents an agent in a distributed opinion retrieval system using Java RMI (Remote Method Invocation), specializing in critical thinking.
    Influencer
    The Influencer class represents an influential agent in a distributed opinion retrieval system using Java RMI (Remote Method Invocation).
    Polarimeter
    Polarimeter class for measuring polarization based on agent opinions retrieved via socket communication.
